"Ullrich Haupt (actor born 1915)" 0 Ullrich Haupt (October 15, 1915 – November 23, 1991) was an American-born German actor. His father, also named Ullrich Haupt, was a German actor who worked in Hollywood films, but he returned to Germany following his father's death in 1931.
